    <section>
      <div class="text-box">
        <h2>Search profile</h2>
        <p>At PetMatch, we simplify pet adoption by connecting you with your ideal furry friend through a smart, personalized platform. Together, we create joyful, lasting relationships while giving shelter animals the loving homes they deserve.</p>
        <p>Discover your ideal pet companion through our matching algorithm that considers your lifestyle and preferences to find the perfect match for you.</p>
        <a href="">Get started</a>
      </div>
     <img src="static/photos/catenhondhome.jpeg" alt="Cat and dog in grass">
